sequenceDiagram
    participant M as Main
    participant G as Game
    participant S as Snake
    participant F as Food
    M->>G: create game
    G->>S: create snake
    G->>F: create food
    M->>G: start game
    loop Game Loop
        G->>S: move snake
        G->>F: check if snake eats food
        G->>S: grow snake if food eaten
        G->>F: respawn food if eaten
        G->>M: update score and high score
    end
    opt Pause Game
        M->>G: pause game
        M->>G: resume game
    end
    G->>M: end game
